commit.message:
Refactor basic Collection support

Rename Collection class to SimpleCollection
Add exclusions to the collection relation so the collection works with groups.
Add relations parameter to the constructor to provide vustome relations
Add a way for each class to define relation providers
Add support for multiple url generators
Add relation/embed exclusion config using the serializer exclusion strategies

Allow to build absolute URIs

Add a third parameter named 'absolute' to the Route

Fix #44

Merge pull request #40 from adrienbrault/xml-hal

Add XmlHalSerializer, extend embed config, use jms metadata for xml element name

Remove unused variable

Also detected by insight
Add Embed xmlElementName support to the configuration layer
Some fixes, but omg ... it's working! :p
